<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Belshazzar le a bawi hawi thongkhat rawldanghnak puai ah, 'Sui hrai in
 manzu cu an ding,' tiah Cathiang chungah aa tial, Siangpahrang innpi
 chungah zan i an sopawt ling ah, Vanpang cung i kut a cuangmi nih an
 thlasen a hlauh hna.

[C1]
   Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, &quot;Na
   chambau ko,&quot; maw &quot;Na tling ko,&quot; tinak khi dah a si hnga, Vanpang cungah
   kut nih ca a tial.

[V2]
 Saltang miraltha Daniel, mi zapi hmai ah a dir, Mi-porhlaw
 siangpahrang pa cu a palhnak ruangah a sik. Catial cu an rel tikah mi
 zapi thihnak a si, Siangpahrang pennak a rawk cang, ti in tialmi ca a si.

[C2]
   Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, &quot;Na
   chambau ko,&quot; maw &quot;Na tling ko,&quot; tinak khi dah a si hnga, Vanpang cungah
   kut nih ca a tial.

[V3]
 Dinnak lei ah zumh ngamhnak a ngeihning cu zoh tuah u, Thlarau nih
 Daniel cu thawnnak a rak pek ca ah a si, Judea ram a inn in maw a
 saltannak hmun in dik, A Pathian vanpang cung kuttial sullam cu a rak
 hngalh cang.

[C3]
   Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, &quot;Na
   chambau ko,&quot; maw &quot;Na tling ko,&quot; tinak khi dah a si hnga, Vanpang cungah
   kut nih ca a tial.

[V4]
 Kan tuahsermi vialte zong Pathian kut nih a tial dih, Maw misual na
 lungthin vialte lianngan Jesuh sinah pe, Mi kip cungah a tlung laimi
 biaceihnak ni ah cun, Kan sualnak vialte cu vanpang cungah tial a si ve
 lai.

[C4]
   Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, Pathian kut vanpang ah a cuang, &quot;Na
   chambau ko,&quot; maw &quot;Na tling ko,&quot; tinak khi dah a si hnga, Vanpang cungah
   kut nih ca a tial.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>VANPANG CUNG KUTTIAL CH38</title>
<hymn_number>38</hymn_number>
</song>